246	### 1.4 Props
247	
248	```rust
249	/// The props for the `ImageCropper` component.
250	#[derive(Clone, Debug, PartialEq, HasId)]
251	pub struct Props {
252	    /// Component instance ID.
253	    pub id: String,
254	    /// Controlled crop area.
255	    pub crop: Option<CropArea>,
256	    /// Default crop area for uncontrolled mode.
257	    pub default_crop: CropArea,
258	    /// Image source URL.
259	    pub src: String,
260	    /// Aspect ratio constraint.
261	    pub aspect_ratio: AspectRatio,
262	    /// Initial zoom.
263	    pub zoom: f64,
264	    /// Minimum zoom.
265	    pub min_zoom: f64,
266	    /// Maximum zoom.
267	    pub max_zoom: f64,
268	    /// Circular crop mask.
