845	## 2. Anatomy
846	
847	```text
848	ImageCropper
849	├── Root              (required -- role="application")
850	├── Image             (required -- the source image, possibly transformed)
851	├── Overlay           (required -- semi-transparent mask outside crop area)
852	├── CropArea          (required -- the selected region, focusable)
853	│   ├── Grid          (optional -- rule-of-thirds grid lines)
854	│   └── Handle x 8    (required -- resize handles on corners and edges)
855	├── ZoomSlider        (optional -- zoom control)
856	├── RotationSlider    (optional -- rotation control)
857	├── ResetTrigger      (optional -- reset to default crop)
858	└── Label             (required -- describes the cropper)
859	```
860	
861	| Part           | Element    | Key Attributes                                                   |
862	| -------------- | ---------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
863	| Root           | `<div>`    | `role="application"`, `aria-roledescription="cropper"`           |
864	| Image          | `<img>`    | `aria-hidden="true"`, zoom/rotation CSS custom properties        |
865	| Overlay        | `<div>`    | `aria-hidden="true"`, semi-transparent mask                      |
866	| CropArea       | `<div>`    | `tabindex="0"`, `ars-touch-none`, position CSS custom properties |
867	| Grid           | `<div>`    | `aria-hidden="true"`, rule-of-thirds overlay                     |
868	| Handle         | `<div>`    | `aria-label="Resize {position}"`, `ars-touch-none`               |
869	| ZoomSlider     | `<input>`  | `role="slider"`, `aria-valuenow/min/max`                         |
870	| RotationSlider | `<input>`  | `role="slider"`, `aria-valuenow/min/max`                         |
871	| ResetTrigger   | `<button>` | `aria-label` from messages                                       |
872	| Label          | `<label>`  | Labels the cropper                                               |
873	
874	**`touch-action: none` requirement:** The CropArea element and all resize Handle elements
875	MUST include `class="ars-touch-none"` from the companion stylesheet. Without this,
876	touch-initiated dragging and resizing on mobile devices triggers browser scroll/pan
877	instead of producing pointer events.
