879	## 3. Accessibility
880	
881	### 3.1 ARIA Roles, States, and Properties
882	
883	| Attribute              | Element              | Value                                         |
884	| ---------------------- | -------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
885	| `role="application"`   | Root                 | Custom interaction model                      |
886	| `aria-label`           | Root                 | From `messages.label` (default: "Crop image") |
887	| `aria-roledescription` | Root                 | `"cropper"` -- generic type descriptor        |
888	| `role="slider"`        | ZoomSlider           | Zoom control                                  |
889	| `role="slider"`        | RotationSlider       | Rotation control                              |
890	| `aria-label`           | Handle               | `"Resize {position}"` from messages           |
891	| `tabindex="0"`         | CropArea             | Keyboard focusable for arrow-key nudging      |
892	| `aria-hidden="true"`   | Image, Overlay, Grid | Decorative/structural elements                |
893	
894	### 3.2 Keyboard Interaction
895	
896	| Key         | Element  | Action                    |
897	| ----------- | -------- | ------------------------- |
898	| Arrow keys  | CropArea | Nudge crop area (1% step) |
899	| Shift+Arrow | CropArea | Large nudge (10% step)    |
900	| +/-         | Root     | Zoom in/out               |
901	| r/R         | Root     | Rotate +/-90 degrees      |
902	| h           | Root     | Flip horizontal           |
903	| v           | Root     | Flip vertical             |
904	
905	### 3.3 Screen Reader Announcements
906	
907	The cropper includes a visually-hidden live region (`aria-live="polite"`) that
908	announces crop area changes:
909	
910	- "Crop area moved" -- after arrow-key nudging
911	- "Crop area resized" -- after handle resize
