971	## 5. Library Parity
972	
973	> Compared against: Ark UI (`ImageCropper`).
974	
975	### 5.1 Props
976	
977	| Feature                        | ars-ui                           | Ark UI                                           | Notes                                         |
978	| ------------------------------ | -------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ | --------------------------------------------- |
979	| `crop` / `defaultCrop`         | `crop` / `default_crop`          | `initialCrop`                                    | Equivalent; ars-ui adds controlled mode       |
980	| `aspectRatio`                  | `aspect_ratio`                   | `aspectRatio`                                    | Equivalent                                    |
981	| `cropShape`                    | `circular`                       | `cropShape` (circle/rectangle)                   | Equivalent                                    |
982	| `zoom` / `minZoom` / `maxZoom` | `zoom` / `min_zoom` / `max_zoom` | `zoom` / `minZoom` / `maxZoom`                   | Equivalent                                    |
983	| `rotation`                     | via `SetRotation` event          | `rotation` / `defaultRotation`                   | Equivalent                                    |
984	| `flip`                         | `flip`                           | `flip` / `defaultFlip`                           | Equivalent                                    |
985	| `fixedCropArea`                | --                               | `fixedCropArea`                                  | Ark prevents crop area resizing; niche        |
986	| `nudgeStep`                    | 0.01 (hardcoded)                 | `nudgeStep` / `nudgeStepShift` / `nudgeStepCtrl` | Ark has configurable nudge steps              |
987	| `zoomStep`                     | 0.1 (hardcoded)                  | `zoomStep`                                       | Ark has configurable zoom step                |
988	| `zoomSensitivity`              | --                               | `zoomSensitivity`                                | Ark has pinch zoom sensitivity                |
989	| `minWidth` / `minHeight`       | 0.05 (5% min)                    | `minWidth` / `minHeight`                         | Ark has pixel-based min; ars-ui uses fraction |
990	| `maxWidth` / `maxHeight`       | --                               | `maxWidth` / `maxHeight`                         | Ark has max crop dimensions                   |
991	| `src`                          | `src`                            | --                                               | ars-ui has image source prop                  |
992	| `disabled`                     | `disabled`                       | --                                               | ars-ui has disabled state                     |
993	| `translations`                 | `messages`                       | `translations`                                   | Equivalent                                    |
994	
995	**Gaps:** None critical. `fixedCropArea` and granular nudge/zoom step props are minor configurability that adapters can override.
996	
997	### 5.2 Anatomy
998	
